I'd love to hear
your thoughts on--

00:05:40.760 --> 00:05:42.260
SADHGURU: They
did not define it.

00:05:42.260 --> 00:05:42.720
JONATHAN BERENT: They did not.

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:44.370
OK, well I was just going
to ask you what's missing.

00:05:44.370 --> 00:05:45.240
[LAUGHTER]

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:48.030
So you can start.

00:05:48.030 --> 00:05:55.800
SADHGURU: With all due respect,
they spoke about intent,

00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:58.760
right intent.

00:05:58.760 --> 00:06:03.290
They spoke about the
right kind of thoughts,

00:06:03.290 --> 00:06:09.340
Emotions, attitudes, and
to some extent actions.

00:06:09.340 --> 00:06:13.040
There is no
consciousness in this.

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:18.040
If we are understanding
that the way we think,

00:06:18.040 --> 00:06:21.690
feel, and act is of
a consciousness, no.

00:06:21.690 --> 00:06:22.920
It is lie.

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:26.990
We are mistaking a plant.

00:06:26.990 --> 00:06:31.090
We are mistaking the
flower for the soil.

00:06:31.090 --> 00:06:34.183
We are mistaking
expressions for the source.

00:06:38.700 --> 00:06:40.730
This is something that's
happening everywhere,

00:06:40.730 --> 00:06:42.570
not just here.

00:06:42.570 --> 00:06:44.270
People think by
changing attitudes,

00:06:44.270 --> 00:06:45.670
their consciousness will change.

00:06:45.670 --> 00:06:47.340
No.

00:06:47.340 --> 00:06:49.400
By changing attitudes,
certain actions

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:53.550
will change-- yes,
positive, beneficial.

00:06:53.550 --> 00:06:58.100
But it is not truly
transformative.

00:06:58.100 --> 00:06:59.500
Change will happen.

00:06:59.500 --> 00:07:01.450
Transformation will not happen.

00:07:01.450 --> 00:07:05.330
If I have to define a
distinction between change

00:07:05.330 --> 00:07:09.780
and transformation, change
means the residue of the past

00:07:09.780 --> 00:07:11.760
will still remain.

00:07:11.760 --> 00:07:14.480
A transformation means
nothing of the past

00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:17.280
will remain, which is
what is needed today

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:19.390
if you want to
create a new world,

00:07:19.390 --> 00:07:23.790
if you want a new generation
to have a fresh life.

00:07:23.790 --> 00:07:26.550
It's been expressed
in so many ways.

00:07:26.550 --> 00:07:30.930
Being in this part of the world,
what their family are with,

00:07:30.930 --> 00:07:34.347
generally, someone said,
leave the dead to the dead.

00:07:34.347 --> 00:07:35.263
It's very significant.

00:07:37.980 --> 00:07:42.740
This is not coming
out of recklessness.

00:07:42.740 --> 00:07:45.700
This is not coming
out of unconcern.

00:07:45.700 --> 00:07:48.410
But this is coming
with the concern

00:07:48.410 --> 00:07:52.300
that you must be a fresh life.

00:07:52.300 --> 00:07:55.080
You can learn many
things from the past

00:07:55.080 --> 00:07:58.290
about how to conduct yourself.

00:07:58.290 --> 00:08:03.610
But there is nothing to learn
from the past about how to be.

00:08:03.610 --> 00:08:08.060
Because you are a
complete life by yourself.

00:08:08.060 --> 00:08:12.200
You don't have to learn how
to be a life from the past.

00:08:12.200 --> 00:08:15.730
Maybe you have to learn
how to be a good engineer.

00:08:15.730 --> 00:08:18.480
Maybe you have to learn
how to be something else

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:20.160
in the society from the past.

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:24.680
But you don't have to learn
how to be a life from the past,

00:08:24.680 --> 00:08:27.410
because past has
nothing to do with this.

00:08:27.410 --> 00:08:31.250
This is a fresh life, and
this is a complete life.

00:08:31.250 --> 00:08:34.640
Consciousness is that
dimension, which is

00:08:34.640 --> 00:08:37.100
the very source of who we are.

00:08:37.100 --> 00:08:42.650
Our intentions, our actions,
our thoughts, and our attitudes

00:08:42.650 --> 00:08:44.970
are a consequence of that.

00:08:44.970 --> 00:08:48.400
Or in other words, we are
trying to fix the consequence

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:51.830
without fixing the source.

00:08:51.830 --> 00:08:55.240
Now all these distinctions
of variety of things

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:57.860
that they said, gender
discriminations,

00:08:57.860 --> 00:09:04.060
racial discriminations,
every kind, OK?

00:09:04.060 --> 00:09:07.326
Somebody is Hindu,
somebody is a Muslim,

00:09:07.326 --> 00:09:09.200
somebody is a Googler--
it becomes a religion

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.576
after some time, believe me.

00:09:10.576 --> 00:09:12.240
[LAUGHTER]

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:14.710
Second generation, they
will become a religion

00:09:14.710 --> 00:09:15.910
by themselves.

00:09:15.910 --> 00:09:17.810
Yes.

00:09:17.810 --> 00:09:22.850
I'm saying you will see a
football match going on.

00:09:22.850 --> 00:09:25.870
It's like a religion,
two different clubs.

00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:28.610
They're willing to fight
and kill each other.

00:09:28.610 --> 00:09:34.800
Just a game. [CHUCKLING] So
where does this come from?

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:38.830
See, the nature of
being human is this.

00:09:42.115 --> 00:09:43.240
If you give me two minutes.

00:09:47.820 --> 00:09:52.760
There are four
dimensions of our mind.

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:59.160
In modern societies, the
nature of our education

00:09:59.160 --> 00:10:02.500
has constipated our
mind in such a way

00:10:02.500 --> 00:10:06.310
because we are just largely
using just one dimension,

00:10:06.310 --> 00:10:08.850
which we call as the intellect.

00:10:08.850 --> 00:10:11.140
The other dimensions
of mind, if I

00:10:11.140 --> 00:10:13.530
have to use Indian
terminology, it

00:10:13.530 --> 00:10:18.750
means buddhi, ahankara,
manas, and chitta.

00:10:18.750 --> 00:10:21.820
What buddhi means
is the intellect.

00:10:21.820 --> 00:10:22.940
You do what you want.

00:10:22.940 --> 00:10:28.810
The nature of the intellect is
to slice things open and see.

00:10:28.810 --> 00:10:32.180
If you leave the world in
the hands of your intellect,

00:10:32.180 --> 00:10:34.870
your intellect will chop
it into a million pieces

00:10:34.870 --> 00:10:37.630
and will want to chop it
into further micro pieces

00:10:37.630 --> 00:10:40.330
and want to chop it into
further micro-micro pieces,

00:10:40.330 --> 00:10:43.760
depending upon how
sharp your intellect is.

00:10:43.760 --> 00:10:47.660
The sharper your intellect,
the more you dissect the world.

00:10:47.660 --> 00:10:51.050
You cannot stop it, because that
is the nature of the intellect.

00:10:51.050 --> 00:10:52.870
And it's good.

00:10:52.870 --> 00:10:55.520
So you must apply
intellect only to know

00:10:55.520 --> 00:10:57.860
the material aspects of life.

00:10:57.860 --> 00:11:01.900
You can't know life this way.

00:11:01.900 --> 00:11:03.617
If I want to know you,
can I dissect you?

00:11:03.617 --> 00:11:04.450
JONATHAN BERENT: No.

00:11:04.450 --> 00:11:11.930
[LAUGHTER]

00:11:11.930 --> 00:11:17.795
SADHGURU: But if a doctor wants
to know some aspect of you,

00:11:17.795 --> 00:11:20.530
materially what's wrong with
you, he will take a biopsy.

00:11:20.530 --> 00:11:23.910
And in a way, he opens
it up and looks at it.

00:11:23.910 --> 00:11:25.250
It's OK on that level.

00:11:25.250 --> 00:11:29.180
But I can't know you as a
person by dissecting you.

00:11:29.180 --> 00:11:31.930
I can't know you as a
life by dissecting you.

00:11:31.930 --> 00:11:34.540
I can know a part
of your body maybe.

00:11:34.540 --> 00:11:38.050
Similarly, I can know parts of
the world to make use of it.

00:11:38.050 --> 00:11:41.180
But I can't know life as such.

00:11:41.180 --> 00:11:45.490
So intellect has
been over-energized

00:11:45.490 --> 00:11:47.880
in the last 100, 150 years.

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:52.710
This is a European impact on
the rest of the world, where we

00:11:52.710 --> 00:11:55.110
think our thought is supreme.

00:11:55.110 --> 00:11:59.320
Someone went to the extent
of saying, I think so I exist

00:11:59.320 --> 00:11:59.860
or whatever.

00:11:59.860 --> 00:12:03.280
[LAUGHTER]

00:12:03.280 --> 00:12:05.318
I want to ask all of
you a simple question.

00:12:08.510 --> 00:12:12.360
Tell me, is it because
we exist we may think?

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:14.240
Or is it because
we think we exist?

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:16.280
Which way is it?

00:12:16.280 --> 00:12:18.610
Hello?

00:12:18.610 --> 00:12:22.090
Because we exist, we may
think, because people

00:12:22.090 --> 00:12:26.630
are in such a state of
mental diarrhea all the time.

00:12:26.630 --> 00:12:28.120
Nonstop it's going on.

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:32.810
They think it's more of an
existence than existence.

00:12:32.810 --> 00:12:34.620
But my head is
all the time empty

00:12:34.620 --> 00:12:36.970
unless I want to
think about something.

00:12:36.970 --> 00:12:38.520
So I know a thought
is not necessary.

00:12:38.520 --> 00:12:40.550
I can just live here
without a thought.

00:12:40.550 --> 00:12:41.750
When I want, I will think.

00:12:41.750 --> 00:12:43.370
Otherwise, I'll keep quiet.

00:12:43.370 --> 00:12:45.740
Just like my hand--
if I want to use it,

00:12:45.740 --> 00:12:47.220
otherwise I keep it here.

00:12:47.220 --> 00:12:49.690
Similarly, you must be able
to do this with your mind.

00:12:49.690 --> 00:12:52.929
Just because you lost control
over your mind and you think

00:12:52.929 --> 00:12:54.470
it's everything
because it's entering

00:12:54.470 --> 00:12:56.803
into every aspect of your
life where it has no business.

00:12:59.560 --> 00:13:02.700
Thought has been
over-energized by people.

00:13:02.700 --> 00:13:06.750
And the very nature of the
thought is such that if you

00:13:06.750 --> 00:13:10.170
think it must be logical,
it cannot be any other way.

00:13:10.170 --> 00:13:13.660
Well, what somebody is thinking
may look illogical to you,

00:13:13.660 --> 00:13:16.460
but they have found
their own logic.

00:13:16.460 --> 00:13:19.100
The most extreme person
that you have met,

00:13:19.100 --> 00:13:22.040
within himself or herself,
they have their own logic.

00:13:22.040 --> 00:13:23.460
Isn't it so?

00:13:23.460 --> 00:13:26.740
They're not speaking illogically
as far as they're concerned.

00:13:26.740 --> 00:13:29.010
They have found their
own kind of logic.

00:13:29.010 --> 00:13:31.950
Logic means it needs two.

00:13:31.950 --> 00:13:34.300
Logic means it needs division.

00:13:34.300 --> 00:13:36.930
Now logically you're
trying to arrive

00:13:36.930 --> 00:13:38.320
at inclusive consciousness.

00:13:38.320 --> 00:13:40.620
It's not going to happen.

00:13:40.620 --> 00:13:43.025
Because you're using
a knife to stitch.

00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:48.100
This is not going to work.

00:13:48.100 --> 00:13:50.890
If you use a knife to
cut, it's efficient.

00:13:50.890 --> 00:13:53.230
You use a knife to
stitch things together,

00:13:53.230 --> 00:13:55.630
you will only tear
it up further.

00:13:55.630 --> 00:13:57.110
So my thought and
your thought, I

00:13:57.110 --> 00:13:59.870
am telling you, whatever
